		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1316" width="436" height="174" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">复活期间，双方<span color="#ffdfbf">+300%</span><span>全抗；一方杀着蓄力期间，另一方</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+300%</span><span>全抗。<br/>冻结条：总进度100%。受到</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>攻击</span><span color="#bfffff">+2%</span><span>，在第</span><span color="#99ffff">1</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">2</span><span>/</span><span fontFamily="SDK_TW_Web" color="#99ffff">≥</span><span color="#99ffff">3</span><span>次大招期间，触发冻结</span><span color="#bfffff">+30%</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffff">+50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffff">+90%</span><span>，在2.6s内继续触发冻结只会</span><span color="#bfffff">+6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffff">+10%</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffff">+18%</span><span>；<br/>上述进度会受到多人模式影响(×1/0.9/0.83/0.8)；<br/>若受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击，或者在后的杀着蓄力期间自身超时解冻，则</span><span color="#ffbfbf">-50%</span><span>。<br/>填满后若成功触发机制，则对应敌方将瘫痪10s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1504" width="433" height="135" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秒杀：若为多人模式，则随机击败一名玩家的前台，剩余玩家的前台<span color="#ffcc99">扣除60%</span><span>生命值。<br/>持续恢复生命值：每0.4s恢复</span><span color="#ffb299">3.2%</span><span>生命值。<br/>在「升扬之王」第</span><span color="#ffcc99">1</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffcc99">2</span><span>/</span><span fontFamily="宋体" color="#ffcc99">≥</span><span color="#ffcc99">3</span><span>次杀着期间，所受伤害总和的</span><span color="#ffcc99">50%</span><span>若大于「升扬之王」的</span><span color="#ffcc99">10%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffcc99">15%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffcc99">20%</span><span>生命值，则采用前者作为最终扣血伤害，最大不超过「升扬之王」</span><span color="#ffcc99">20%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffcc99">25%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffcc99">30%</span><span>的生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
