				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">王抡起大剑，朝玩家方向砍下，造成<span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="398" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">王突然朝玩家方向突进，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害；接着原地旋转，持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">33%,<br/>19.8%,9.9%,3.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">王背上「象」，持剑一跃落地，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害；接着王将剑拔出，产生的冲击波造成</span><span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="422" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">王指使后一同进行一连串攻击：<br/>后进行近战划击，造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害；王掏出「象」置于地面，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害；后发射连续的雷片子弹，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">28%,<br/>14%~2.8%</span><span>伤害；王扔出的「象」落地爆炸，对落点范围内造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1503" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后协助王进行下落攻击：<br/>王跳至「车」上，后引爆「车」将王炸飞，并引剑重重下落，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。引爆「车」将造成</span><span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>的超载伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/门扉前的弈局2.assets/Image_28.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/门扉前的弈局2.assets/Image_29.png')" x="720" y="361">
