			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="21" y="1086" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="22" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">王</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="21" y="1145" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="22" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">后</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后扔下一枚「马」并爆裂，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后从地上唤出6枚排成环状的「兵」，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害，然后「兵」又落回地面，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后协助王进行烧灼攻击：<br/>后召唤一个水漩涡，持续牵引角色并持续施加<span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>附着，同时王手持「马」作喷火器，持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">30%,15%,7.5%,<br/>3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="440" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">王移至场地中央，高举大剑并开始蓄力，期间双方将持续附着<span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>，后在场地降下小雨，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">28%</span><span>伤害；12s王蓄力完成，大剑落下，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">125%</span><span>伤害并</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffccbf">秒杀</span><span>前台。期间王会</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffccbf">持续恢复生命值</span><span>。<br/></span><span color="#ffe599">破解方法：</span><span>只需将</span><span textDecoration="underline">冻结条</span><span>填满即可，王损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1183" width="425" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后移至场地中央，开始吟诵，四周出现巨大水幕，期间我方将持续附着<span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>，王在场地内横冲直撞，接触造成</span><span color="#ff9999">40%</span><span>伤害；16s后吟唱完成，水幕奔涌，</span><span color="#ffccbf">秒杀</span><span>前台。<br/></span><span color="#ffe599">破解方法：</span><span>将</span><span textDecoration="underline">冻结条</span><span>填满并引导王撞击即可，后损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">18%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">23%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">28%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
