			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">后召唤4枚雷电棘刺，对前方的目标造成<span color="#ffacff">40%,20%,8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
